=== Prep ===
 yum -y install squashfs-tools

=== Unpack ===
<pre>
mkdir 1
cd 1
zcat ../core.gz | cpio -i -H newc -d
</pre>

=== Repack ===
 find | cpio -o -H newc | gzip -9 > ../core.gz

